- Notes
So finally I got some time over to do this shit. Took a while longer to edit than expected tho, not the frag part (finished that weeks ago) but the intro/outro which was tricky. Thanks Saxne for the AE support, ReactoR for the camera and netropa for the fine filming. Also a big thanks to dr0nt who made the awesome logo. Oh, and Blixtra for being mjaukatt.


- Technical stuff
OK, maybe 3000 bitrate was a bit overkill but hey, 23MB/min! Not too shabby. x264 makes wonders. To play the movie use VLC or install the files included in the zip. Note: during the ffdshow installation you should only check decoding of x264, nothing else. Also un-check post processing in the install, if checked. For audio decoding, un-check all boxes.
